com.cyc.kb.client

Class VariableImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.kb.client.KbObjectImpl
      • com.cyc.kb.client.VariableImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.cyc.kb.KbObject, com.cyc.kb.Variable

    public class VariableImpl
extends KbObjectImpl
implements com.cyc.kb.Variable
    A Variable object is a facade for a #$CycLVariable in Cyc KB. A character strings starting with a ? followed by one or more alpha numeric characters. This is used to represent a variable in a sentence.
